<|bos|><|user|>

<|/user|><|assistant|>
I'll configure Nginx for completed_product.app:

<|exec|>
$ sudo apt install -y nginx
<|/exec|>

Setting up nginx...
<|/exec_result|>
<|exec|>
$ cat > /etc/nginx/sites-available/completed_product.app << 'EOF'

    listen 6807;
    server_name completed_product.app;
    root /var/www/completed_product.app;
    index index.html;
}
EOF
<|/exec|>

(no output)

$ sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/completed_product.app /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/

(no output)
<|/exec_result|>
<|exec|>
$ sudo nginx -t
<|/exec|>
<|exec_result|>
Syntax OK
<|/exec_result|>
<|exec|>
$ sudo systemctl restart nginx
<|/exec|>
<|exec_result|>
(no output)
<|/exec_result|>
<|exec|>
$ curl -I http://localhost:6807
